title: O'Neill Evolution 2012 - Men's Semi-Finals
description: The rushes edit from the power riding in the O'Neill Evolution Semi Final. Snowfall, spins, slides and powder slashes. A feel of what it like for everyone experiencing it live here in Davos on site as all the action went down to define the 16 who would make it through to the Finals. Check out the top three winning kicker tricks, and winner of the Semi's, Stale Sandbech's winning and glory run trick - just for fun!
